","tid":2132560,"uid":6777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9feb6a920609297c7c305ac2428e1e5db1c7107a","tid":2132560,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"之前睇過好似話古代少生智慧齒<br />\nD食物種類唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n古代人無好似現代咁又汽水又色素之類既野<br />\n<br />\n食既野都係天然，對牙齒既傷害無咁大<br />\n<br />\n只要keep 住用鹽或石灰石膏墨魚骨之類既野刷牙，就已經keep 到<br />\n<br />\n不過呢，因為古代人容易有暴力事件，打仗打交都多d,所以智慧齒比較有用，就算年輕果陣有牙甩左，都可以靠4隻智慧齒<br />\n<br />\n當有比較多空位生智慧齒，就會降低少少無咁痛啦"},{"pid":"d595c16a07b776a02af2be355abd911feaeee4ba","tid":2132560,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"有錢你驚咩"},{"pid":"a0b84df89a22f000acb8a17b103f600d57c5d232","tid":2132560,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"男人老狗小小痛都忍唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6504f22b5f14924f9f6400ba8bd95b753bad17","tid":2132560,"uid":206468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"前幾日牙痛去照x光，順便睇下有無需要剝，嗰牙醫同我講牙根未發育哂，而且有機會生得哂，可以再睇下情況點先，開左Ｄ消炎藥比我，我好似比佢撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128024073d380950adaa2ba49edd1c5fee1a14e2","tid":2132560,"uid":141269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6504f22b5f14924f9f6400ba8bd95b753bad17","tid":2132560,"uid":206468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"前幾日牙痛去照x光，順便睇下有無需要剝，嗰牙醫同我講牙根未發育哂，而且有機會生得哂，可以再睇下情況點先，開左Ｄ消炎藥比我，我好似比佢撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:54:18.000Z","msg":"成日被牙醫撚"},{"pid":"052234ab21ac40200253fbe21ac378493ddfec5e","tid":2132560,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:55:32.000Z","msg":"開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/